      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I\u2019m parting with my well-loved car, and it\u2019s honestly been a dream to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape, super clean inside, and ready for many more miles of adventures with its next owner. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
