    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between spirited performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, showing only the expected minor stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, and every feature\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine performs smoothly and reliably, backed by a comprehensive service history that documents regular oil changes and proactive maintenance. We have recently performed a full multi-point inspection and a fresh fluid service to ensure the car is turn-key ready. This is a solid, honest example of a well-loved car that drives with the same precision it did when it first left the showroom. Non-smoker owned and garage-kept, it represents an excellent value for a driver who appreciates quality and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 36800.0,
